import React from "react";
import {
  FooterContainer,
  FooterAbout,
  FooterLogoContainer,
  FooterLogo,
  UnorderList,
  List,
  FooterWidget,
  FooterContact,
  Title,
  Side
} from "./footer.styles";
import Logo from "../../assets/img/logo.png";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterContainer>
      <FooterAbout>
        <FooterLogoContainer to="/">
          <FooterLogo src={Logo} />
        </FooterLogoContainer>
        <UnorderList>
          <List>Address: 60-49 Road 11378 New York</List>
          <List>Phone: +65 11.188.888</List>
          <List>Email: hello@colorlib.com</List>
        </UnorderList>
      </FooterAbout>
      <FooterWidget>
        <Title>Useful Links</Title>
        <Side>
          <Link to="/">About Us</Link>
          <Link to="/">About Our Shop</Link>
          <Link to="/">Secure Shopping</Link>
          <Link to="/">Delivery information</Link>
          <Link to="/">Privacy Policy</Link>
          <Link to="/">Our Sitemap</Link>
        </Side>
        <Side>
          <Link to="/">Who We Are</Link>
          <Link to="/">Our Service</Link>
          <Link to="/">Projects</Link>
          <Link to="/">Contact</Link>
          <Link to="/">Innovation</Link>
          <Link to="/">Testimonials</Link>
        </Side>
      </FooterWidget>
      <FooterContact>b</FooterContact>
    </FooterContainer>
  );
};

export default Footer;
